                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.01/160: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-11-06T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 6, 1919, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3686. For <persName corresp="#p_PFL">Polk</persName>.</p>
                <p>Your 4796, October 24, 11 a.m.</p>
                <p>In spite of recent untoward events in Siberia, consideration is still being given
                    to the possibility of recognizing <persName corresp="#p_KAAV1"
                        >Kolchak</persName> in case he survives the present crisis.</p>
                <p>I shall keep you currently informed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
